[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    282[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mProblem:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m The canonical Part D Star Ratings adherence measure for statins is "Medication Adherence for Cholesterol (Statins)" (PQA measure ADC, formerly PDC-STA). The denominator is members ≥18 years with two or more fills of any statin during the measurement year. There is [38;2;180;142;173m*[38;2;180;142;173mno[38;2;180;142;173m*[38;2;191;97;106m CVD diagnosis requirement; primary-prevention statin users are included on equal footing with secondary-prevention users.[K
