[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    472[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m The unread atorvastatin reminder paragraph: [38;2;180;142;173m*[38;2;180;142;173m"The text doesn't address the actual barrier (she has a belief about side effects from a family member's experience), so it doesn't move the behavior. The plan logs it as 'delivered' and 'no response,' which counts as a successful outreach in the operations dashboard, and counts as nothing in the actual world where Maria still has uncontrolled cholesterol."[38;2;180;142;173m*[38;2;191;97;106m The "successful outreach in the operations dashboard, nothing in the actual world" framing is the chapter's clearest articulation of intermediate-vs-outcome metric confusion before the Honest Take even gets to it.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    473[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;180;142;173m*[38;2;180;142;173m"This is what medication adherence intervention looks like in practice. The data identifies the *what[38;2;180;142;173m*[38;2;191;97;106m: which medications, which patients, which adherence levels. The hard work is identifying the [38;2;180;142;173m*[38;2;180;142;173mwhy[38;2;180;142;173m*[38;2;191;97;106m, and matching the [38;2;180;142;173m*[38;2;180;142;173mwhy[38;2;180;142;173m*[38;2;191;97;106m to the right intervention."* Cleanest one-paragraph framing of the recipe's central thesis.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    474[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m The Star Ratings cut-point distortion paragraph is the chapter's most direct moral hazard discussion. [38;2;180;142;173m*[38;2;180;142;173m"Both can't win when capacity is finite. The recipe's policy weights make this explicit; teams should make the trade-off conscious, document it, and accept that 'we are optimizing primarily for Star Ratings' is a defensible answer if it's said out loud and reviewed, while 'we are not thinking about it and our model converged on the 75-79 band because that's where the engagement data was densest' is not."[38;2;180;142;173m*[38;2;191;97;106m This is exactly the post-mortem-confession voice that distinguishes the chapter.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    475[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;180;142;173m*[38;2;180;142;173m"The thing that surprises people coming from retail recommendation backgrounds is how much of adherence is about *staff capacity[38;2;180;142;173m*[38;2;191;97;106m, not patient targeting."* The "the model is useless if the pharmacist queue has been at capacity for three months" landing is right.[K
